ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.villagephotos.com/extern/406910.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> GV and HV</span><hr size=1> I used Horrifying Visage last night for the first time really, its a spell I had missing and when i got it had to wait until then to use it.   What do we think about this spell?  it really did seem to make a difference but you just never can tell, I just wanted feedback of you guys to see if you think HV enables someone to keep that extra aggro needed .  Is it worth hitting the MA with HV. I think it is <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  but would like to hear what you guys think.<br>
<br>
Also with Ref to Glamorous visage,  Im yet to use it to be honest as Ive been looking for it for a while.  Ive not really looked into how long this lasts and when i shall personally use it,  I wouldnt mind some feed back on this either <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I am thinking maybe good for BIG MOB versus CLERIC hehe ie to keep aggro off on first CH but im really not sure if this is how one would choose to use it.  <br>
<br>
Would be cool to get some advise <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  thx guys <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=215357"target="_blank"><img src="http://www.vmottram.btinternet.co.uk/Tigi.jpg"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ullientylln.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llientylln</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#330000>(7/17/02 10:09:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.prophesy.ca/eq/enchanters/Llientylln.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GV and HV</span><hr size=1> Yes, Glam Visage on the clerics for that first CH on a big mob fight helps a bit, also I use it on myself if I'm having to tash and haven't had time to pop up Beguiling Visage or if I'm trying to also land a cripple on said bid mob heh. I have yet to be summoned when I remember to use those first. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
 <p><p><center><embed src="http://luther.wordcrafters.org/images/lliesig.swf" WIDTH=350 HEIGHT=120 quality="high" pluginspage="http://www.macromedia.com/shockwave/download/index.cgi?P1_Prod_Version=ShockwaveFlash" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=130411" target="_blank"><br><i>What I'm wearing... </i></a></center>
</p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ucazroy00.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cazroy00</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#330000>(7/17/02 9:08:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GV and HV</span><hr size=1> The short duration and long recast time doesn't make it worth taking up a spell slot in most situations for me.  Also the fact that myself and most of the people I group with know how to control thier agro.  So these type of spells stay at the back of my spell book.<br>
<br>
Cazroy Gelorstedt<br>
60th Season Enchanter<br>
Raindancer of Karana<br>
&lt;Silver Daggers&gt; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ullientylln.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llientylln</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#330000>(7/17/02 10:03:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.prophesy.ca/eq/enchanters/Llientylln.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GV and HV</span><hr size=1> Glam. Visage doesn't have a long recast time - only Beguiling. Glam. loads up fairly quickly <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   so you can swap it out easily.<br>
<br>
I can usually get two debuff attempts off before the spell fades. (cripple * 2 if resisted the first, etc.) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ullientylln.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llientylln</A> at: 7/17/02 10:04:26 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ukelthanmindwalker80.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KelthanMindwalker80</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#330000>(7/21/02 7:14:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GV and HV</span><hr size=1> only place ive used them is UP, the aggro on those mobs is insane. With gv on myself, i can tash as soon as the tank starts to melee, and slow if no shammy without catching a summon. with bv ive tashed before the tank even turned around to attack the pull, no aggro<br>
<br>
also, chain casted hv on a pally at a UP raid for a few reg mobs, he took aggro off the MT without stuns or taunt<br>
<br>
ide say these line of spells is for use when VI decides to shaft us with extreame aggro zones and mobs <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gourthauer>Gourthauer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#330000>(11/22/02 7:29:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GV and HV</span><hr size=1> I use HV a lot in situations where we only have one tank and I need to slow quickly. Slowing sometimes requires tashing and I get serious agro (as any Enchanter can atest to). When I keep HV on the tank, be it monk or warrior, it has been obvoius to me that the mob switches back to the tank MUCH faster than without. I know spell slot real estate is precious, but I consider HV to be a very good use of one of them. <br>
<br>
-Master Omahr (61 Phantasmist) The Rathe <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showPrevMessage?topicID=213.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showNextMessage?topicID=213.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.threadControl?topicID=213.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=213.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=213.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub136.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm11">General<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm12">Equipment<option value="eqenchantersrealmspells">Spells<option value="eqenchantersrealmfaqs">FAQs<option value="eqenchantersrealmstories">Stories<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm7">Quests<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm9">Tradeskills<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm13">Auctions<option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm14">Weapons & Ar